                </FooterDetails>
                <Header>Catalog of U.S. Government Publications (CGP)</Header>
                <Paragraph>The CGP is a searchable Federal publications catalog that contains descriptive information on recent and historical publications, as well as links to some complete documents. Users may search  the catalog by agency, keywords, subject, and title.</Paragraph>
            </EntitySourceOfInformation>
            <EntitySourceOfInformation EntitySourceOfInformationId="3506" SortOrder="10">
