                    <Footer/>
                    <WebAddress>https://www.govinfo.gov/app/collection/crecb</WebAddress>
                </FooterDetails>
                <Header>Congressional Record</Header>
                <Paragraph>The "Congressional Record" (CR) is the official record of the proceedings and debates of the U.S. Congress. When the U.S. Congress is in session, it is published daily. The CR's publication history started in 1873 and continues to the present. The first link leads to CR bound editions from 1873 to 2016.</Paragraph>
            </EntitySourceOfInformation>
