                <Header>Federal Depository Library Program (FDLP)</Header>
                <Paragraph>Libraries that participate in the FDLP maintain a basic collection of key sources of information for supporting the general public's right to know about the essential activities and workings of the Federal Government.</Paragraph>
            </EntitySourceOfInformation>
