                <Header>News / Press Releases</Header>
                <Paragraph>The GPO posts the latest news and maintains a news archive, from 1997 to the present, on its website. Phone, 202-512-1957. Fax, 202-512-1998.</Paragraph>
            </EntitySourceOfInformation>
