                </FooterDetails>
                <Header>Oversight</Header>
                <Paragraph>The Office of the Inspector General from the GPO posts reports and data on Oversight.gov, a text-searchable repository of reports that Federal Inspectors General publish. The Council of the Inspectors General on Integrity and Efficiency operates and maintains the website to increase public access to independent and authoritative information on the Federal Government.</Paragraph>
            </EntitySourceOfInformation>
